Image captured by webcam is shown in window to perform different gestures in front of webcam. 

Hardware Platform : Pentium 3 processor or above,128 MB RAM,
Operating System :  Win 98/2000/XP.
Software component: Microsoft Visual Studio 6.0  
Libraries: OpenCV

1. Webcam
2. Monitor
3. CPU
4. Webcam Stand
5. Hand Gloves
